===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# [[uncut]] [[jade]]
#* {{zh-x|夫{fú} 珠玉，人主 之 所-急 也。和 雖 獻 璞 而 未 美，未 為{wéi} 主 之 害 也；然 猶 兩-足 斬 而 寶 乃 論，論 寶 若 此 其 難 也。|Indeed, pearls and gems are what the lord of men wants badly. Though Ho presented the '''{{w|Mr. He's jade|uncut jade}}''' to the Throne, before it was made beautiful, he was never a harm to His Majesty. Nevertheless, it was only after both his feet had been cut off that the treasure was acknowledged. That to establish an opinion of a treasure should be so difficult!|ref=Hanfeizi}}
# {{alternative form of|zh|朴}}: rat meat which has not been air-dried
